frames.caption: A large, menacing wolf with glowing yellow eyes stands prominently in a moonlit forest. The full moon illuminates its dark fur, creating a dramatic and eerie atmosphere. Surrounding trees frame the scene, enhancing the sense of wilderness and mystery.
